# agent_play — optional local overrides. Copy to `.env` (gitignored).
# NO API KEY REQUIRED: the harness drives the game through the Claude Code CLI, billed to your
# Pro/Max subscription. Run `claude /login` once. ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is ignored by the harness —
# set one only if OTHER tools in this repo need API-key billing.

# Optional overrides (uncomment as needed):
# AGENT_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8
# GODOT=godot
# AGENT_GODOT_PROJECT=
# AGENT_PORT=8099
